Notes:

# For applying Roles Based Security using @Secured

1. Enable Global security in Security Configuration file
@EnableGlobalMethodSecurity(prePostEnabled = true)

2. Mark the api with roles
@PreAuthorize("permitAll")
@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ROLE_USER')")
@PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole('ROLE_USER', 'ROLE_ADMIN')")
@PreAuthorize("denyAll")
@PreAuthorize("isRememberMe()")  -- Yet to verify
@PreAuthorize("isAuthenticated()")
@PreAuthorize("hasPermission(targetObject, permissionObject)") -- Yet to verify